 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Rules Violations<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Article III.A.(4) \u2013 Published Policies<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.B.(2)a. \u2013 Hazing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.B.(2)b. \u2013 Hazing Policy<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Findings<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Found responsible.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Date Resolved: 1\/14\/2026<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Individuals Responsible: &lt;5<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Arrests<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>None<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sanctions<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Disciplinary Probation through November 2026<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Educational Assessment Fee<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Campus Hazing Speaker<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Leadership Education (Executive Team, New Member, and Recruitment Leadership)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reduction of Social Privileges \u2013 Spring 2026<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reduction of Social Privileges \u2013 Fall 2026<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Loss of Privilege: Block Seating (Fall 2026 &#8211; 2 games)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Security Enhancements \u2013 Chapter House<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Chapter and Organizational Education (Alcohol and Hazing Prevention)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Establishment of Harm and Risk Reduction Committee Establishment of Alumni Advisory Board<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fall 2025 Description Sigma Pi new members were subjected to physical exercises, line-ups and personal servitude. New members were required to dress in matching attire and carry specific items on their person.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[8],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-768","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-8"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v